{"tid":956133,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普:股市現處便宜水平 是入市良機","createTime":"2018-12-26T04:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T13:01:44.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"ea87671375afa4b46a07cdaaf52102240b3bcd0f","tid":956133,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T04:39:15.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普在聖誕節接受傳媒訪問時，繼續炮轟聯儲局，指加息太急。<br />\n<br />\n不過，特朗普贊同財長努欽在星期日與金融業巨擘的行政總裁通電話，以及周一與救市小組討論市場流動資金的行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特朗普認為，美國股市現時處於便宜水平，是投資者入市的良機。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，個人認為聯儲局的加息決定是錯誤的，因為步伐過急。他認為，現時利率已處於正常水平，而且對大部分美國人民而言，現時利率合宜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2023533/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%3A%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E7%8F%BE%E8%99%95%E4%BE%BF%E5%AE%9C%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3+%E6%98%AF%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%82%E8%89%AF%E6%A9%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2023533%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%253A%25E8%2582%25A1%25E5%25B8%2582%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%2599%2595%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E5%25AE%259C%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25B9%25B3%2B%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25B8%2582%25E8%2589%25AF%25E6%25A9%259F&d=nlZSAbnHmEPvOkfLRhKZ1AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=52f1c87b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2023533/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%3A%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E7%8F%BE%E8%99%95%E4%BE%BF%E5%AE%9C%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3+%E6%98%AF%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%82%E8%89%AF%E6%A9%9F</a>"},{"pid":"90235520218a9870b308581ced3bb50a1c09d24e","tid":956133,"uid":19725,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T04:41:25.000Z","msg":"做開商人 做緊總統都忍唔住要講股市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d2ba59f8daeebac06aa44d68dc6a90876c97e0","tid":956133,"uid":22422,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T04:47:38.000Z","msg":"President Xi is my friend <br />\n所以都係不了"},{"pid":"004fe88e3eadaee4175a76b6fe46